Installation

1. Install the Python Requests library from https://github.com/kennethreitz/requests
2. Install livestreamer from https://github.com/chrippa/livestreamer
3. Install VLC from https://videolan.org/vlc/
4. Change TWITCH_USERNAME to your Twitch.tv username in twitch-line.py
5. run `/path/to/twitch-line.py` or alias it or add it to your path

Notes
- You can't see chat
- If stream crashes you have to reopen from the cli
- If you follow over 100 people and they are all live, you will only see 100
- No commercials (streamers don't get revenue.  Only use if you sub or donate in other ways)
- Kappa

Future plans
- Background the livestreamer call
